Text: Comanche Request Cc Jenny Could you have your team run a brief past three weeks or so CDR report on and add mailto to Mailsweeper filter for Comanche Thanks Rus

RE Comanche Request Phase II Cc Jenny Thanks for your help with Comanche As a result of some of the earlier work we are now interested in further review of a few individuals Could you have your team pull as much of the historical email as possible for the following Please advise how far back you can go with this Also we would like to include this name in a mailsweeper filter for future email traffic We do want to compartment this a little from our overall Comanche effort so we ask that you help us with a second mailbox for this material My boss Scott Tholan will be the lead on the second mailbox and needs your help getting started Could you help him with the following A Add the current mailbox mbxprojcomm to his desktop B Create a second Comanche mailbox with the above filter and add to his desktop C Install the pst viewing software on Scotts machine D Provide the above historical email to Scott Scott can be reached on should your team need to contact him We are on a very short timeframe and need to accelerate this as soon as possible so we greatly appreciate your help As always thanks for your support and please let one of us know if you have any questions Thanks Rus Comanche WebTrends reports wwwrecruiterconnectioncom wwwdwiccom wwweliasassociatescom wwwemeraldstaffingcom Thanks and let me know if you have any questions Rus Rus Woody Smith Street Suite Houston TX
